{"word":"Ashtaroth","slug":"ashtaroth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ashtaroth</b> <a href=\"#/H6252\">H6252</a> <br/> 1. Plural form of Ashtoreth<br/> <a href='S:Ashtoreth'>Ashtoreth</a><br/> 2. A city<br/> - The capital city of Bashan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=1&verse=4'>Deu 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=9&verse=10'>Jos 9:10</a> <br/> - Giants dwell at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=4'>Jos 12:4</a> <br/> - Allotted to Manasseh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=31'>Jos 13:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=6&verse=71'>1Ch 6:71</a> <br/> - Possibly identical with Ashteroth Karnaim<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=5'>Gen 14:5</a> "}]}